channel.title: Model section over the years(Lots of pictures)[Take a look its free!]
channel.description:
First off this topic is to show that not all the good modellers started good. Some really did work at it to get better, while looking threw all these pictues(with shrogg) it took us back to when this section wasn't about poly frames or count, but about just making and showing off models and having people tell you what they think not how much they hate it. Also this just proves you can't become a good modeller overnight but that it takes time and you got to work for it.
But all that sappy shit aside lets look at progress!
Credits to SilentCJ for a full reformat of the topic. If anyone would like adding and I (SilentCJ) consider you to be worthy, drop me a message or post on the topic with your images and I'll add you on.
